<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”灯光熄灭时，凯蒂和乔伊尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“手电筒在哪里？”妈妈问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但没人听见她的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风听起来像火车在房子上空呼啸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们能听到风从树之间穿过的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“低下头。”爷爷喊道，避难所的门嘎吱作响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的杰利！”乔伊叫道，“外面一定很可怕。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦古也很害怕。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她能感觉到狗狗在她怀里发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，呼啊！可怕的声音消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面一片寂静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在里面，每个人都开始说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人受伤吗？”爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“风很大。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好大的龙卷风啊！”凯蒂叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“结束了吗？”乔伊问道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须找到杰利！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“手电筒在哪里？”妈妈又问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂在盒子里找到手电筒打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>光照亮了她的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她摇着手电筒，看见了妈妈、爸爸、爷爷和乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都很好，组长。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>收音机吱呀作响，妈妈拿起它调节声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布恩镇的恶劣天气已经过去了。”播音员说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们重复一遍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国家气象局发布了一项全面解除警报。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布恩镇的龙卷风警报已经结束。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看。”乔伊说。“是阳光。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>光透过避难所的门照了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦古从凯蒂怀里溜出来，跑上楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，我们去看看怎么样了。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他爬上楼梯，推开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来，宝贝们。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在外面，凯蒂和乔伊看到一个破花盆和一把弯曲的折叠椅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>花园的一段栅栏不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到处都是树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“房子没有被吹走！”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是个好消息。”爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但空房间有一扇窗户坏了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷从地上捡起一个东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有一只我的园艺手套。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去园子看看吧。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有小鸡们。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂和乔伊跑在前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“生菜毁掉了！”凯蒂大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“豆豆都掉在泥里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊边沿着栅栏跑，边大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别管青豆了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷、妈妈和爸爸追上双胞胎，看着菜园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的西瓜籽肯定被冲走了。”乔伊叹了口气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以再买些种子。”爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里的东西我们都可以修复的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听到小鸡们的声音了！” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来了！”她边走边喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她打开门时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小鸡们急急忙忙地跑了出来，又吵又叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里一切看起来都很好。”她大喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去看看树屋吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转向山坡，跑了几步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！”她大喊着朝山上望去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她又跑了几步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“树屋的一部分被毁了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她突然想起杰利还没找到呢，不禁大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的猫咪。”她小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去看看。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和乔伊匆匆赶到树屋，爬上了楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸把树枝从窗户上拿开，看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到一些碎木板。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们可以修复一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们只需要一套好的工具和团队合作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对吗，搭档？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她的眼睛睁得大大的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你听到那个声音了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>喵！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰利还活着！”乔伊大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸跪下，看了看一堆树枝和木头下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出手，拉出一只湿乎乎的灰猫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把颤抖的杰利抱在怀里，探出窗外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多诺万一家人都没事！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五个人、六只鸡、一条狗和一只了不起的猫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>